t spotlight here.                           GO  ... to our events  Please note that, due to the COVID-19 pandemic, we have cancelled our Spring Programming and look to reschedule in the fall.     Email us if you have an event that you would like to see publicized in our weekly bulletin.                            © 2013 UIC Institute for Research on Race & Public Policy   | Contact | Site Map |  designed by Creative Well 